description:
A standard iron shield. It offers some protection. It's
better than nothing!
name: Shield

description: Clothes that will keep you warm.
name: Cloth

description: A versatile accessory that strengthens its wearer.
name: Emerald Ring

description: An extremely fortified shield.
name: Heavy Scale Shield

description: Armor made from a giant reptile's scales.
name: Abyssal Plate

description: A gift from the rulers of the Earth.
name: Sky Essence

description: Armor made from a giant reptile's scales.
name: Abyssal Helm

description: A lightweight bulletproof exosuit.
name: Enigmatic Armor

description:
All that's left of this ring is a sky blue jewel 
connected to a brittle frame.
name: Blue Ring

description:
A basic framework that offers little protection from
the outside world.
name: Damaged Exosuit

description:
A ring designed to withstand the elements.
Grants +10% ice damage resistance.
name: Frost Ring

description:
A hat that covers part of your face. Won't stop a 
bullet, but at least it makes you look cool.
name: Tactician's Hat

description:
Basic tactician armor. Nice and breathable for flexible
movements.
name: Tactician's Armor

description: A ring that moderately increases the AGI of its wearer.
name: Fury of the Wind

description: Special armor composed of magical fibers.
name: Standard Mage Robes

description:
Light armor specifically designed for heroes. Much more
protective than standard clothes.
name: Valkyrie Armor

description: Heavy plated armor fit for a Lancer.
name: Platemail

description:
Experimental Lancer armor. It might not be very tough,
but it will increase the power of your healing spells.
name: Sage's Plate

description:
A wool scarf. Slightly protects from the cold. 
+5% ice damage resistance.
name: Warm Scarf

description: A shield fitted with a large spike in the center.
name: Spike Shield

description: Just like what Barry Cotter used to wear.
name: Wizard's Hat

description:
Now that's more like it. Robes designed for a
practician of dark magic.
name: Dark Mage's Robes

description:
Mages can't take a hit. Help them out with this shield!
Nullifies 10% of physical damage.
name: Stormshield

description:
Flexible but protective. The strength of this armor
comes from dragon's scales that line the exterior.
name: Light Dragonplate

description:
Standard issue protective headgear that is distributed
to town guards worldwide.
name: Traditional Battle Helm

description:
A shield made from a strong metal: mythril. It is much
stronger than a standard iron shield.
name: Mythril shield

description:
You'll be unstoppable with this armor on. 
Neutralizes 20% of almost all types of damage.
name: Guardian's Platemail

description:
An experimental armor designed for Lancers. Grants
+20% TP charge rate, and makes healing spells stronger.
name: Gaia's Sacred Armor

description:
This helmet was created to protect Lancers on their
way to slay dragons. Provides 10% fire resistance.
name: Juggernaut's Helm

description:
Contains a crystal blessed by powerful mages. Heals 5%
of your max HP per turn.
name: Ring of Regeneration

description:
The user is immune to all negative status effects
except for death.
name: Pendant of Brilliance

description:
Gauntlets designed to protect your hands during battle.
Generate +5 TP per turn.
name: Power Gauntlets

description:
Experimental phase-shifting technology. The wearer 
has a 25% chance to dodge all types of damage.
name: Phase-Shifting bracelet

description: The user's critical rate is increased by +10%.
name: Lucky Ribbon

description: Gain 10% lifesteal from physical attacks.
name: Fang Necklace

description:
Gauntlets that were designed to make spellcasting more efficient. 
The MP cost for all skills will be reduced by 25%.
name: Magic Gauntlets

description:
A simple knight's helmet. Offers basic protection from your 
enemies.
name: Training Helmet

description:
The energies of this ring rapidly reconstruct damaged body
parts. What sorcery is this?
name: Genesis Ring

description:
A powerful shield whose energies guard against physical
and magical attacks
name: Deflector Shield

description:
A custom-crafted shield fitted with a dragon's ruby.
The wearer is immune to the "frozen" status.
name: The Shield of Drakes

description:
Kendra's soul allows you to drain energy from living things.
Heal 15% of damage done from physical and magical attacks.
name: Soul Eater Pendant

description:
These gauntlets were designed for everybody to use. 
They will reduce the MP cost of all skills by 50%.
name: Sorcerer's Gauntlets

description:
A powerful cape, blessed with a goddess' divine power.  
Start every battle with 100TP and resist negative statuses.
name: Etherea's Light

description:
An experimental armor designed for Lancers. Grants
+20% TP charge rate, and makes healing spells stronger.
name: Gaia's Sacred Armor(Proxy)

description: Testing only.
name: Admin Pendant

description:
Gauntlets designed for powerful warriors.
Grants an extra +10TP per turn.
name: Gauntlets of Might
